{"tid":1839293,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"老母板audio問題","createTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T11:04:16.000Z","uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a06c2ed1ee35bfabc9090999a99a8bba44f654eb","tid":1839293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"原先用B85M-G，<br />\nCarousell買左塊二手Z87-A。<br />\n上完塊板舊audio driver好似用唔到，<br />\n所以uninstall舊，裝官網audio driver，<br />\nBIOS都有enable Realtek Audio Controller。<br />\n部機detect到我set speaker（插主機板3.5mm）<br />\n同埋headphone（插機箱前面板3.5mm），<br />\n但係兩樣野都只係出滋滋聲。<br />\n是咪on board audio打左柴？<br />\n如果係，唔加sound card既情況下是咪無可能整得翻？"},{"pid":"486e1deffad0937b4ee4ed073aa5cda049147b7c","tid":1839293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求教"},{"pid":"1afcc0c2598785b6cbf89a599bca307621100b5f","tid":1839293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"700c179364e02afc1aa34c9fc586414e22742f89","tid":1839293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"補充：<br />\n宜家暫時用緊顯示卡hdmi過audio落mon，set speaker插mon。<br />\n系統係win10。<br />\nSpeaker、headphone插翻舊板正常使用。<br />\n塊板其餘所有功能應該正常，未試digital audio output。<br />\n我試曬所有analog audio，輸入輸出都唔得。"},{"pid":"fd07020abe9553685d27ef8f3f4085f3682bef0d","tid":1839293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2e403c102a23aa59e2d28c86c9f42ff38874493","tid":1839293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"好彩淨係壞audio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}